title: U.S. Presidential Candidate Ramaswamy Takes Potshot at DeSantis Bitcoin Remark
description: The largest cryptocurrency is suddenly a talking point in the 2024 race, after Florida Governor Ron DeSantis declared he would “protect the ability to do things like Bitcoin” during the launch of his campaign on Twitter on Wednesday.
